《'''暴风雨'''》（{{lang-en|The Tempest}}）是依据[[威廉·莎士比亚|威廉·莎士比亚]]的同名戏剧改编而成的一部[[美国电影|美国电影]]。该片导演[[萨姆·泰勒|萨姆·泰勒]]，约翰·巴里摩尔和卡米拉·霍恩担任主演，于1928年上映。<ref name="NY Times">{{cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/48992/Tempest/details |title=NY Times: Tempest |accessdate=2008-12-07 |work=NY Times |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017062518/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/48992/Tempest/details |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Home|url=https://aficatalog.afi.com/|access-date=2022-05-05|work=AFI Catalog|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101025411/https://aficatalog.afi.com/}}</ref> 

